                  </hi>. I am an inspector of the City police force</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186709230081"></xptr>
               <p>—Obee spoke to me near the Turk's Head on the night of the 9th Sep<lb></lb>tember—we went in and found the three prisoners there; there was also a fourth man.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
