                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">recalled</hi>). <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Did you make a memorandum at the time of the address which Evans gave? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I did, but I cannot find it now—21, Busby Street, is the address he gave me.</p>
